  <brief_title>Study of the Efficacy and Safety of Lonidamine for the Treatment of Symptomatic Benign Prostatic Hyperplasia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Phase 3, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study of the Efficacy and Safety of Lonidamine for the Treatment of Symptomatic Benign Prostatic Hyperplasia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
